[I] A video wallpaper program for wlroots based wayland compositors

[T] mpvpaper is a wallpaper program for wlroots based wayland compositors, such
[T] as sway. That allows you to play videos with mpv as your wallpaper.

[U] https://github.com/GhostNaN/mpvpaper

